    "description": "A structured mesh independence study was conducted on the centrifugal pump geometry using three successively refined grids (coarse, medium, fine) at the nominal operating point (5 L/min, 3000 RPM). Grid convergence index (GCI) was computed for velocity magnitude and wall shear stress. The study was executed by the CFD team lead and documented in internal report VER-2024-07.",
